1
00:00:36,180 --> 00:00:40,940
=Ancient Bracelet=

2
00:00:41,340 --> 00:00:44,380
=Episode 23=

3
00:00:44,420 --> 00:00:46,660
=Do You Wish to Be My Brother's Bride?=

4
00:00:48,350 --> 00:00:50,200
I should find a place
to settle in first.

5
00:00:51,790 --> 00:00:52,630
Wait.

6
00:00:59,150 --> 00:01:00,110
Have we

7
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:01,640
met before?

8
00:01:02,150 --> 00:01:04,480
Why do you feel so familiar to me?

9
00:01:06,040 --> 00:01:06,880
Ying Du,

10
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:08,400
we...

11
00:01:11,870 --> 00:01:13,200
(We were once deeply in love.)

12
00:01:13,350 --> 00:01:14,680
You know my name.

13
00:01:17,950 --> 00:01:18,790
(Indeed.)

14
00:01:19,070 --> 00:01:21,510
(At this time, he hadn't met me.)

15
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:24,120
Yes.

16
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:26,150
I know more than just your name.

17
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:29,480
I know you are cool outside
but warm inside,

18
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:31,430
a fool who'd give his life for love.

19
00:01:33,070 --> 00:01:33,950
A fool?

20
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:41,680
Come in.

21
00:01:43,040 --> 00:01:43,880
Snow's falling hard.

22
00:01:44,310 --> 00:01:46,230
Do you plan on standing
in the wild all day?

23
00:01:59,740 --> 00:02:09,020
(Wuyue tribe)

24
00:02:21,190 --> 00:02:22,030
Miss,

25
00:02:22,310 --> 00:02:24,360
why are you crying nonstop?

26
00:02:24,590 --> 00:02:26,870
Did my brother just make you cry?

27
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:28,800
I just...

28
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:31,680
I just miss home.

29
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,680
Every time I cry,

30
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:34,910
my brother picks plum blossoms

31
00:02:34,910 --> 00:02:37,080
and makes sweet congee to cheer me up.

32
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,130
Du,

33
00:02:38,150 --> 00:02:39,470
can you make some

34
00:02:39,470 --> 00:02:40,560
for her

35
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:41,590
to cheer her up?

36
00:02:56,430 --> 00:02:57,280
Little one,

37
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:59,000
he's your brother?

38
00:02:59,030 --> 00:03:01,080
Then where are your parents?

39
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,400
Why

40
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:04,150
haven't I seen them around?

41
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:06,630
I've never met them.

42
00:03:06,910 --> 00:03:08,310
I only have my brother.

43
00:03:09,310 --> 00:03:11,870
Do you want to be my brother's bride?

44
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:13,360
I...

45
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,740
Well, I...

46
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:19,800
Little one,

47
00:03:20,750 --> 00:03:21,910
what's your name?

48
00:03:22,150 --> 00:03:22,990
Fengwu.

49
00:03:23,150 --> 00:03:25,240
My brother gave me that name.

50
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:27,120
Feng as in whispering winds,

51
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:29,400
and Wu as in secret dealings.

52
00:03:35,870 --> 00:03:36,710
What a coincidence.

53
00:03:37,590 --> 00:03:40,280
Grandmother used to call me Fengwu too.

54
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:02,680
You shouldn't have come.

55
00:04:10,750 --> 00:04:11,590
Your Majesty.

56
00:04:11,910 --> 00:04:13,150
You can't change anything.

57
00:04:14,190 --> 00:04:15,520
Why wager everything on one move?

58
00:04:15,750 --> 00:04:16,680
But, Your Majesty,

59
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,480
Puluo State needs you.

60
00:04:18,830 --> 00:04:19,750
(He is...)

61
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:21,750
(Luo Cheng of this lifetime.)

62
00:04:22,310 --> 00:04:23,630
I spent three years

63
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:25,950
helping Puluo State end the turmoil,

64
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:28,070
turning a small frontier tribe

65
00:04:28,190 --> 00:04:29,870
into what is now the Puluo State.

66
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:32,040
Puluo no longer needs me.

67
00:04:32,390 --> 00:04:34,600
According to our pact, my duty now is

68
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:37,560
to protect Fengwu.

69
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:40,960
Your Majesty,

70
00:04:41,060 --> 00:04:41,830
four years ago,

71
00:04:41,841 --> 00:04:43,760
what kind of pact did you make
with the Goddess?

72
00:04:43,950 --> 00:04:45,240
May I know the truth?

73
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:46,390
I promise

74
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:48,630
never again to disturb your life
with Fengwu.

75
00:04:56,390 --> 00:04:57,390
Four years earlier,

76
00:04:57,866 --> 00:04:59,160
Puluo suffered a crushing defeat.

77
00:04:59,160 --> 00:05:00,310
Thousands of comrades

78
00:05:01,070 --> 00:05:02,680
were trapped deep within enemy lines,

79
00:05:02,950 --> 00:05:04,040
with their fate unknown.

80
00:05:04,190 --> 00:05:05,480
To rescue them,

81
00:05:05,630 --> 00:05:07,510
I sought the help of the Goddess.

82
00:05:08,870 --> 00:05:10,120
I foresaw that my daughter

83
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:12,310
would face a fatal calamity.

84
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:14,390
If you are willing
to make a pact with me,

85
00:05:15,190 --> 00:05:16,240
protect her forever,

86
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:18,480
and help her overcome all misfortune

87
00:05:18,630 --> 00:05:20,630
after my death,

88
00:05:20,630 --> 00:05:21,600
(Goddess Xingyue)

89
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:22,630
I shall grant you

90
00:05:22,630 --> 00:05:24,000
my supreme power

91
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:26,390
to aid you through Puluo's crisis.

92
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:27,870
Do you accept that?

93
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:32,310
If it can bring thousands of soldiers
back to life,

94
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:35,070
I'll do whatever it takes.

95
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:40,920
I beg of you.

96
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:15,240
For Puluo State,

97
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,560
I have fulfilled my mission.

98
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:19,070
But for Fengwu,

99
00:06:19,070 --> 00:06:20,390
I must protect her

100
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:22,000
and honor my promise.

101
00:06:24,870 --> 00:06:25,710
Your Majesty,

102
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:27,160
I understand.

103
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:39,190
(Ying Du made a pact with the Goddess.)

104
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:41,720
(But why did he later become the ruler)

105
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,600
(and even cross paths with me?)

106
00:06:45,510 --> 00:06:46,920
You've heard the whole story.

107
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:48,190
Still planning to hide?

108
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:51,830
Are you talking about me?

109
00:06:52,510 --> 00:06:53,360
Who else could it be?

110
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:01,320
I...

111
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:04,160
I didn't mean to eavesdrop.

112
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:05,190
I just...

113
00:07:08,430 --> 00:07:09,360
Just what?

114
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:13,430
I only wanted to know

115
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:16,600
what pact you made with the Goddess.

116
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:21,000
Who exactly are you?

117
00:07:21,270 --> 00:07:22,270
Where did you come from?

118
00:07:23,070 --> 00:07:24,680
Why do you know me so well?

119
00:07:26,510 --> 00:07:27,350
I...

120
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:30,760
Du.

121
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:32,830
Careful now.

122
00:07:32,830 --> 00:07:34,120
How did you get out?

123
00:07:35,630 --> 00:07:37,070
Du, let her go.

124
00:07:37,070 --> 00:07:39,000
She hasn't agreed

125
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:40,270
- to be your bride.
- Fengwu...

126
00:07:40,270 --> 00:07:41,920
Bride? Fengwu is making that up.

127
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:42,880
We...

128
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:50,680
You can turn back time too?

129
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:53,120
Who exactly are you?

130
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:54,870
What's your name?

131
00:07:54,870 --> 00:07:55,710
Zhaoli.

132
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:56,870
My name is Zhaoli.

133
00:07:56,870 --> 00:07:58,390
Ying Du, don't forget me.

134
00:07:59,060 --> 00:08:01,620
(Year 11 of Rongxi)

135
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:04,750
Why am I

136
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:07,750
still here?

137
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:12,120
What are you doing here?

138
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:17,720
You look so familiar.

139
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:19,070
Have we met

140
00:08:19,243 --> 00:08:20,723
(9-year-old Fengwu)
somewhere before?

141
00:08:21,430 --> 00:08:22,270
Zhaoli,

142
00:08:22,729 --> 00:08:24,516
have you finished picking
the plum blossoms?

143
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:35,160
It's you.

144
00:08:35,766 --> 00:08:37,143
I've waited for you for four years.

145
00:08:38,910 --> 00:08:40,320
At last, you've come.

146
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:45,150
You've been waiting for me?

147
00:08:52,760 --> 00:08:53,610
Zhaoli,

148
00:08:53,630 --> 00:08:54,470
come here.

149
00:08:59,510 --> 00:09:01,000
Ying Du, what did you just call her?

150
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,320
Zhaoli.

151
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:04,390
Four years ago, you suddenly vanished.

152
00:09:04,670 --> 00:09:05,505
Since then,

153
00:09:05,516 --> 00:09:06,510
in my brother's dreams,

154
00:09:06,510 --> 00:09:08,120
he'd been calling your name,

155
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:10,030
lost and restless all day long.

156
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:11,630
So, I took the name Zhaoli.

157
00:09:11,630 --> 00:09:13,200
That way, when he calls for Zhaoli,

158
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,630
he won't be reminded of you.

159
00:09:14,630 --> 00:09:16,840
Since you refuse
to be my brother's bride,

160
00:09:17,030 --> 00:09:19,240
please, stay away from him.

161
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:21,960
(Fengwu is Zhaoli,)

162
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:23,440
(which means me.)

163
00:09:24,390 --> 00:09:26,150
Zhaoli, stop talking.

164
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:27,750
(Why don't I remember anything?)

165
00:09:29,870 --> 00:09:31,150
(Could they be Ying Du and me)

166
00:09:31,150 --> 00:09:32,330
(from another time and space?)

167
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:33,680
Zhaoli,

168
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:36,200
no matter what, you must trust Ying Du.

169
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,390
Do not harm him.

170
00:09:38,100 --> 00:09:38,960
Promise me.

171
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:40,000
What are you talking about?

172
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:40,840
Do you remember?

173
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:51,730
♪Snow falls upon my brows,
blurring suddenly♪

174
00:09:53,560 --> 00:09:58,530
♪Memories turn,
forgiving time after time♪

175
00:09:59,990 --> 00:10:03,270
♪Tears or snowflakes, sweet or bitter♪

176
00:10:03,270 --> 00:10:06,170
♪Hard to tell them apart♪

177
00:10:06,690 --> 00:10:11,980
♪Vowing to give you
three lifetimes' happiness♪

178
00:10:11,980 --> 00:10:15,680
♪In this life, I still run toward you♪

179
00:10:16,030 --> 00:10:18,380
♪No matter the homeward journey♪

180
00:10:18,380 --> 00:10:22,420
♪Falling to the deepest place
in your heart♪

181
00:10:22,420 --> 00:10:24,800
♪And that is enough♪

182
00:10:24,800 --> 00:10:28,590
♪Ahead lies a path without snow or wind♪

183
00:10:28,800 --> 00:10:31,560
♪Begonia blooms across the branches♪

184
00:10:31,930 --> 00:10:37,680
♪One more glance
may let love stand still♪

